  <name>WayneWolf</name>
  <summary>Privacy-focused browser with profile templates</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      WayneWolf is a custom-built browser fork based on LibreWolf/Firefox, designed for
      minimalism, maximum privacy, and performance.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Minimalist UI - No distractions, just you and the web</li>
      <li>Maximum Privacy - Fingerprint resistance, WebRTC blocking, DNS-over-HTTPS</li>
      <li>Legacy Compatibility - Unsigned extensions work out of the box</li>
      <li>Performance - GPU acceleration, aggressive caching, zero animations</li>
      <li>Profile Isolation - Three modes: dev, browse, ghost</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      WayneWolf features an advanced profile template system with auto-configured privacy
      settings and extensions for different use cases.
    </p>
  </description>

